        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        One word sentences include only a single word or a single endocentric phrase.
        They are used to express time or place, praise, a discovery, a warning, to address someone, agreement, opposition, or
        a question. 
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=8886' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '危險 wēixiǎn', 'dangerous')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">危险</a>！(Danger)<p/>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3088' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tíxǐng', 'to remind / to call attention to / to warn of')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">提醒</a> (a warning)
        </li>
        <li>
