          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=6445' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問 yíwèn', 'to question / to query')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问</a> (a question)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=285' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hǎo', 'good / very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">好</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3155' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiú', 'ball')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">球</a>！ (Good shot!)<p/>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16665' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '贊嘆 zàntàn', 'to sigh or gasp in admiration / to praise highly')" 
