        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=285' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hǎo', 'good / very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">好</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。 (That's fine.)<p/>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4405' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tóngyì', 'to agree / to consent / to approve')" 
